Technical Details for Privacy Researchers

For those interested in the technical implementation of our privacy-first approach:

Local Storage
• Uses Apple's SwiftData framework for local-only persistence
• Data stored in app's sandboxed container
• Automatically deleted when app is uninstalled

AI Processing
• Utilizes Apple's FoundationModels framework
• Language models run entirely on-device using Apple Silicon Neural Engine
• No API calls to external AI services
• Complies with Apple's on-device privacy requirements

Network Activity
• Zero network requests made by the app
• No servers to connect to
• No API endpoints
• No telemetry or diagnostics sent anywhere
